sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as End User
    participant Device as Demo.DeviceCode
    participant Auth as NexusAuth
    participant Api as Demo.Bff /api/m2m/profile

    Device->>Auth: GET /.well-known/openid-configuration
    Auth-->>Device: 返回 discovery

    Device->>Device: 使用本地私钥生成 client_assertion<br/>aud = /connect/deviceauthorization
    Device->>Auth: POST /connect/deviceauthorization<br/>scope=openid profile offline_access demo_api<br/>client_assertion(private_key_jwt)
    Auth->>Auth: 校验 client_assertion<br/>校验 client 是否允许 device_code
    Auth-->>Device: device_code + user_code + verification_uri

    Device-->>User: 展示 user_code 与 verification_uri
    User->>Auth: 打开 verification_uri 并登录
    Auth->>Auth: 绑定 device_code 与当前用户<br/>用户同意授权
    Auth-->>User: 授权完成

    loop 轮询直到成功或超时
        Device->>Device: 重新生成 client_assertion<br/>aud = /connect/token
        Device->>Auth: POST /connect/token<br/>grant_type=device_code<br/>device_code<br/>client_assertion(private_key_jwt)
        Auth->>Auth: 校验 client_assertion + device_code 状态
        alt 用户尚未授权
            Auth-->>Device: authorization_pending / slow_down
        else 授权成功
            Auth-->>Device: access_token + refresh_token
        end
    end

    Device->>Api: GET /api/m2m/profile<br/>Authorization: Bearer access_token
    Api->>Auth: 使用资源服务器 JWT 校验配置验证 access_token
    Auth-->>Api: access_token 有效
    Api-->>Device: 返回机器客户端信息
